1. Install python 2.7 on your system.

2. Instal OpenCV with the help of following steps:
    	a. Launch a web browser and go to opencv official page. 
      b. Choose a build you want to use and download it. 
      c. Make sure you have admin rights. Unpack the self-extracting archive.
      d. copy the cv.pyd in python27/lib/site_packages.
      
3. Install numpy and pyttsx.

4. Have a webcam attached to your system.

5. Have a steady white background.
